cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.NA, cs.ST

This paper deals with correntropy based regression, which is a machine learning technique. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the statistical properties of the correntropy based regression estimator, which suggests that it could belong to cs.ST (Statistics Theory). The paper also introduces a new type of noise, which could be of interest to researchers in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SI (Signal Processing). Finally, the paper discusses the asymptotic optimal learning rates, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
